  <ul>
    <li><a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/sh7dm/vue-simpleicons/pull/17" rel="noopener">#17</a>: Add missing <code>xmlns</code> attribute to generated SVGs.</li>
    <li><a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/sh7dm/vue-simpleicons/pull/20" rel="noopener">#20</a>: Refactor icon generator for increased performance.</li>
  </ul>
